blog.title: i love you, but honey, i can't sleep

summary:
i feel like the reasoning behind supporting team iron and team cap is really representing the teams themselves
team iron is all...
body:
i feel like the reasoning behind supporting team iron and team cap is really representing the teams themselves

team iron is all about logic and common sense behind everything, a proper reasoning behind certain actions, it sometimes might be a mistake but it is made out of severe trauma

and team cap is like “but i love bucky” over every other actually smart way of dealing with things
